_sText:
Takes place deep below the surface of the island Rookgaard in Minotaur Hell, the Minotaur Mage's Lair.

Counter-Terrorists start out at the Ring of Fire below the Wolf Maze and must defuse the bomb.
Terrorists start out in the Minotaur Mage's room and must bomb the oven!

The map is based on a place from the game Tibia.
